Below is a complete, fast, and extensible way to add optimizer strategy selection for:

DE (already)

SA (ensmallen)

CNE (ensmallen)

PSO (ensmallen)

SPSA (ensmallen)

ADAM (ensmallen, but needs a gradient interface → we’ll add a very fast SPSA-gradient wrapper)

